parser.visitor

Class PropertiesSemanticCheck

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.visitor.ASTTraverse
      • parser.visitor.SemanticCheck
        • parser.visitor.PropertiesSemanticCheck
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ASTVisitor

    public class PropertiesSemanticCheck
extends SemanticCheck
    Perform any required semantic checks on a PropertiesFile (or parts of it). These checks are done *before* any undefined constants have been defined. Optionally pass in parent ModulesFile (or leave null);
